Last weekend for my birthday we thought we’d try a change of scenery and experience a music-filled getaway to Alpharetta, GA. We had a great time listening to @mrbenbostick play a show at this very eclectic venue @matildasmusicunder_the_pines and had some incredible food (@butcherandbrew, @tbb_122, @collettaatl)

I’d definitely recommend visiting #awesomealpharetta this year for their @wireandwoodfest on October 13 and 14. Ben and 30+ other artists will be performing alongside headliners @marcbroussard and @sustoisreal.  

We had a great stay at the Courtyard Atlanta Alpharetta/Avalon Area, and we particularly liked the fact that they had an indoor heated pool. If you need help planning your visit, check out @awesomealpharetta. 

#AlpharettaGA #LiveMusic #Getaway #AlpharettaMusicCity
